        <Meaning id="87caaf72-e7a7-478d-a94b-b30112893639" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Thiếc (kim loại màu trắng xám, mềm, không gỉ, dùng để mạ sắt làm tôn, làm hộp đựng thực phẩm)</Vi>
          <En>A soft, silvery-white, malleable, non-corrosive chemical element (symbol Sn), commonly used to coat other metals to prevent rust, especially in food cans.</En>
          <Example>Food cans are often made of steel coated with a thin layer of tin to prevent corrosion.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
